{"tid":771902,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公司啲新仔真係離撚晒譜","createTime":"2018-08-08T10:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T11:58:38.000Z","uid":34934,"like":3,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6c66cbae77daeb510721dfb5639f341b6157d161","tid":771902,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"上次單野條友俾人炒咗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/766322\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/766322</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住星期一in咗個新仔<br />\n<br />\n第三日就出事<br />\n<br />\n我地星期二OT<br />\n<br />\n個新仔做晒啲野話約咗frd食飯可唔可以早走<br />\n<br />\n話約咗fd打 mon hunt <br />\n<br />\n佢都on撚9 我燥燥地將公司嚟緊一星期既野俾晒佢做叫佢聽朝交<br />\n<br />\n一早醒目合約寫明OT 無補水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住佢成晚無食野話想落街買飯食 <br />\n<br />\n我話我買咗外賣啦兩個鐘後送到，叫佢等陣（其實我嗌一人餐）<br />\n<br />\n之後12點送到嚟，我：「哎呀，送少咗添，你食啦，我唔食。」<br />\n<br />\n條新仔唔敢食最後落街買咗7仔燒賣食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住2點放工佢話搭的士得唔得<br />\n<br />\n我話你住附近咋喎，行返去啦 （公司太子，佢住長沙灣）<br />\n<br />\n咪成日晒公司錢啦，聽朝返工呀記住<br />\n<br />\n點知第日返工有遲無早<br />\n<br />\n返7點叫佢地早15分鐘返黎換<br />\n<br />\n夠膽死遲成半個鐘先返<br />\n<br />\n話佢地兩句就畀晒面色你睇<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母而家我係老細定你係老細呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻罰撚咗佢無lunch佢係出面喊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cb68b51a1b1137674fb55424f232a366ff6600","tid":771902,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"44ac05c304e965a75e510f2b175d6815da3dadcf","tid":771902,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T1